# Ignore generated test outputs under testdata/, but TRACK committed fixtures (e.g. the
# dotgain20 ICC profile test_patch_png needs). The blanket `test/testdata` ignore meant the
# fixture was never committed, so CI / fresh clones failed (#359). Use `/*` so specific files
# can be re-included (a file can't be re-included if its parent dir itself is excluded).
test/testdata/*
!test/testdata/dotgain20.icc
.idea
pyvenv.cfg
