# ...but `manga_translator/utils/panel/lib/` is vendored Kumiko SOURCE (panel detection),
# not a build artifact. The generic `lib/` rule above wrongly ignored it, so it never got
# committed — CI / fresh clones / git worktrees then failed to import it (#359). Track it.
!manga_translator/utils/panel/lib/
!manga_translator/utils/panel/lib/*.py
